afghanistan 's taliban group kidnapped 23 south korean hostages and set a set sunset deadline for south korea to withdraw its troops from afghanistan , or they would kill them .
south korean officials today held talks with the taliban for the first time as time goes by .
however , the taliban said at the same time that the other kidnapped german hostage was in very poor health and had begun to fall into a coma and lack consciousness .
