taliban spokesman hamid aldi said in a telephone interview with afp at an unidentified location : " we are directly contacting the south korean representatives through the tribal elders . "
" we hope the talks will yield results , " ahmar said .
taliban is set to kill south korean hostages in the evening ( 10 : 30 p.m . taiwan time ) .
the guerrillas have already postponed on two occasions .
difficult to gather consensus on maritime dispute the two koreas ' military talks broke up in discord
the three - day high - level military talks between south and north koreas broke up in discord today due to the separation of each side from the maritime boundary .
north korea 's chief representative lieutenant general kim jung - chol said : " we have come to a conclusion on the final day of the talks held in panmunjon . there is no need for these talks that will yield no results . "
kim jung - chol , who was born in red and looked unhappy , attacked south korea for deliberately evading the boundary of the new sea area in order to replace the discussion of the original " northern limit line . "
he pointed out that the " northern limit line " was not legal .
the yellow sea " northern limit line " was drawn up after the us military ended the korean war in 1953 . however , in recent years , it has become the focus of controversy between the two koreas and north korea even more refuses to recognize it .
north korea said thursday that its warships illegally intruded into the waters , triggering tensions and south korea said the accusation was unfounded .
the clash broke out in the local waters in june 1999 , killing dozens of north korean sailors .
similar clashes erupted again in june 2002 , killing six south korean people .
us treasury secretary visits china , environmental protection and exchange rates key concerns
us secretary of the treasury bob allcock arrived in china yesterday for a visit . the united states is making every effort to persuade china to further carry out the necessary economic reform and environmental protection work , especially the issue of renminbi exchange rate , which has attracted much attention .
us diplomats indicated that bob begins his visit to xining , capital of a major province in northwest china .
at present , china has carried out a series of environmental protection projects near qinghai 's largest salt water lake .
bob begins his visit to beijing today , discussing with chinese officials issues such as the progress of the us - china strategic economic dialogue initiated last year .
the us - china strategic economic dialogue " mainly discussed economic , environmental protection , and other issues . the most important thing is the issue of the rmb exchange rate . us congressmen feel that the renminbi value is too undervalued .
the us - china trade deficit is rapidly soaring , pressure is gradually rising in the united states , and congressmen are preparing to take retaliatory actions against their so - called unfair trade policy toward china .
last week , the us senate finance committee in an overwhelming vote passed a motion demanding that the treasury report the list of countries that recognized the exchange rate of the currency " fundamentally miscalculate " and open the door to potential economic sanctions against beijing .
us congressmen said that the renminbi undervalued made the price of chinese goods sold to the united states very cheap and aggravated the trade imbalance between the united states and china . last year , the us trade deficit with china exceeded $232.5 billion .
