dprk , rok reach agreement on developing light industry and underground resources
chinanews , july 8 -
the democratic people 's republic of korea ( dprk ) and the republic of korea ( rok ) today reached an agreement on cooperation in the exploitation of light industry and underground resources .
according to the agreement , the rok will provide the dprk with raw materials for the production of garments and other light industrial products .
during the three - day visit , south korea and the democratic people 's republic of korea ( dprk ) held consultations on cooperation in the development of light industry and underground resources , and finally reached an agreement .
according to the agreement , south korea will provide north korea with raw materials for the production of garments , shoes and perfume , worth 9.8 billion yen .
to this end , the dprk will grant the right of mining three domestic mines to the rok .
on july 25 , the south korean government will use the cargo ship inchon port in the western part of the country to transport the first batch of 500 tons of fiber optic fiber to north korea .
according to the plan , beginning 28 july , the rok and the dprk will jointly investigate the mine in the eastern part of the dprk .
at the end of last month , the south korean government started to launch an aid program to provide 400,000 tons of rice to north korea .
after the dprk indicated that it is willing to actively implement the agreement reached through negotiations among the six countries on closing nuclear facilities , the dprk - rok economic cooperation has become more active once again .
lanzhou bureau of commodity prices explained that the price of beef is limited only because of excessive increase in price .
chinanews , lanzhou , july 10 c
this afternoon , the lanzhou city bureau of commodity prices invited departments concerned to hold a discussion meeting on limiting the price of beef .
at the press conference , it was learned that the municipal bureau of commodity prices and other departments jointly issued the maximum price of a single paper mainly because the price increase in the beef face exceeded the tolerance of most residents .
the price of beef rose 20 percent this time , the fastest since the beginning of the last century , when the price of beef rose for the first time in lanzhou .
" the government 's action is to take into account the economic capability of the general population in the region , and the introduction of the maximum price limit is based on a cost survey , " said the director of the lanzhou city price bureau .
on 26 february , lanzhou city 's bureau of commodity prices , industry and commerce , and health bureau jointly imposed a maximum price limit of beef on the city 's surface price . once the information is revealed , it attracted strong attention .
it is understood that the forum is aimed at extensively listening to the opinions of various circles and soliciting opinions and suggestions on the specific management measures for the next step , and it is also disclosed that lanzhou will hold a news conference tomorrow .
this will be the second news conference on a rise in beef prices in lanzhou city .
ministry of civil affairs punishes china development promotion association for three months
chinanews , july 11 - according to information from the website of the ministry of civil affairs , the ministry of civil affairs imposed a three - month administrative penalty on the china development and promotion council on july 9 .
the punishment order shows that the china association for promoting regional development has the following illegal acts : first , collect membership fees exceeding the standard , and second , collect other fees from non - member units using the receipt of membership fees .
according to an investigation , the annual membership fee of the organization 's member units is 2,000 yuan . between june 2005 and february 2007 , the society issued a total of receipts of its membership fees to more than 20 units . except for the membership fees of one unit , each member received fees ranging from 10,000 yuan to 100,000 yuan . the rest collected fees totaling more than 800,000 yuan . this was a serious violation of relevant regulations .
the ministry of civil affairs , in accordance with article 33 , section 1 , item 8 , of the " regulations on registration and management of social groups , " has imposed administrative penalties on the society for stopping activities for three months within a specified period and sealed up according to law the seal of the society .
