wang yan 's injuries improve " two levels "
" wang yan was already able to sit up on a wooden bench , but she was not too long . otherwise , she would feel dizziness . " wu xiqin , director of the zhejiang sports bureau 's gymnastics center , told this reporter yesterday .
the injury of wang yan , who was injured earlier in the competition , has continued to improve , of which the muscles on the left and on the right top have recovered and increased by " two levels " more than 10 days ago .
on the 4 th of this month , when wang yan was transferred from the cifc ( intensive care ward ) of the shanghai no. 6 hospital to the special needs ward , her right upper limb muscle was 2 to 3 and her upper limbs were grade 1 .
nearly half a month later , wang yan 's upper limb muscles have improved further .
" the doctor said that wang yan 's right hand strength is more than grade 4 , but she is less than normal grade 5 and her left hand muscle is more than level 3 . "
that is to say , in less than half a month , wang yan 's upper limb muscles resumed " two levels . "
wang yan had been able to sit down on her bed for five minutes with the help of a doctor .
originally , the hospital rehabilitation experts planned to let wang yan practice touch - ups under the protection of the rehabilitation bed last weekend .
however , according to the restoration of wang yan 's current stage , the rehabilitation training has to be temporarily postponed .
wu xiqin said that the main purpose of wang yan 's training is to " sit down " and " she can persist in sitting for a while on a wooden bench , but her time is still not too long . " ( by reporter wang chunqiu )
