china loses 52.5 billion yuan in flood prevention , flood control
this reporter has learned from the national flood prevention and drought control headquarters that as of 29 july , 118 million mu of flood and waterlogging across the country had been flooded . among these , 119.15 million people were affected , 652 people died due to the disaster , 45.2 million homes collapsed , and direct economic losses amounted to 52.5 billion yuan .
drought - stricken areas across the country totaled 140 million mu , with 5.88 million people and 4.7 million heads of livestock having temporary drinking water .
on 29 july , the national general headquarters for flood prevention and drought control made an urgent plan to cope with the current grim flood prevention and drought control situation .
they demanded that all provinces along the huai he and the huai he flood prevention headquarters step up control , strengthen the defense of dams during the period of retreat , and win a complete victory in flood prevention and flood prevention on the huai he .
the national general headquarters for flood prevention and drought control , together with financial and agricultural departments , have sent three work groups to the forefront of flood prevention and drought control to guide flood prevention and drought control work in the heavily stricken areas .
currently , flood prevention work on the huai he is being carried out in an intense and orderly manner . flood prevention projects are operating normally . flood discharge on the huai he has also been thrown into the huai he . 268,000 people in the three provinces of henan , anhui , and jiangsu firmly held on the dykes of the huai he .
there is no great danger in the mainstream of the huai he .
heilongjiang , jiangxi , and other provinces started their emergency response to the drought in accordance with their preliminary plans , and drought resistance work is being carried out in a tense and orderly manner .
( by reporter zhao yongping )
taiwan 's " department of justice " denies chen shui - bian 's involvement in elections and demands his explanation
chinanews , july 31 - chen shui - bian questioned legislators on the 30 th their attempt to intervene in the taiwan region 's leadership elections .
on the same day , gao jinzhi , " director of the executive department of the court , " said that the present performance of the judge on the island is inconsistent with what chen shui - bian said and demanded that chen shui - bian give an explanation of his statement .
according to a report by taiwan 's lien - ho pao [ lien - ho pao ] , chen shui - bian questioned judges , procurators , or investigators on 30 august , because of political factors or election considerations , to intervene , influence , or even attempt to influence the election activities of various party candidates . he said that he hoped such a phenomenon would not exist in taiwan , but might be very difficult .
in response to chen shui - bian 's question , weng yuesheng , " president of taiwan 's judicial yuan " , failed to respond in a low - key manner . fan kuang - qun , " secretary general " , sent gao jinzhi to speak on behalf of the " department court . "
gao jinzhi said : the basic law and the " code of judges " of taiwan state explicitly that judges should be allowed to go beyond their parties , not to participate in party activities , and not to campaign for election campaign . judges should be very careful in observing the relevant restrictions , and judges are believed to have done well .
gao jinzhi cited an example to point out that a few years ago , zhang shengxi , judge of the kaohsiung supreme academy of science , attended the kada school course , which was decided by the discipline inspection committee formed for judges because the relevant curricula were of political party tint .
chang sheng - xi once wanted to take part in the primary of the democratic progressive party , but finally decided to give up because of disputes over taking part in the election .
gao jinzhi believes that if the trial of a particular case is conducted , the relief at the level of adjudication cannot be based solely on the outcome of the judgment , then the judge has other political intentions .
germany to lower entry threshold for professionals
xinhua news agency , berlin , july 1st , by reporter huaicheng wang
german minister of education and scientific research shawan said a few days ago that germany should lower the restrictions on the entry of foreign professionals in the " immigration law " and resolve the problem of shortage of professional talent that germany is facing .
according to the oecd report , by the year 2010 , the number of people between the ages of 15 and 64 will decrease year by year .
if there are not enough immigrants , by 2020 , germany 's labor force will decrease by 6 percent .
however , an organization report by the german employers ' federation and the german association of engineers shows that there is a rather large gap of engineers and specialized technical talent in germany 's current labor market .
according to data from the german federal labor bureau , in may this year , the supply gap for engineers in the german labor market was about 127,000 , and the supply gap for technicians was about 9,600 .
in order to protect domestic employment , germany has set a relatively high threshold for attracting talented people from abroad .
germany 's " immigration law " stipulates that professionals in non - eu countries must not have an annual income of 85,500 euros , otherwise they cannot obtain work and residence permits in germany .
shawan proposed to reduce the quota to 40,000 to 60,000 euros .
do not have blind faith in law and the " theoretical circle "
article 8 of the " lawyer law " recently submitted to the standing committee of the national people 's congress for examination stipulates that lawyers may be allowed to practise if they apply for lawyers ' professional titles or equivalent .
( 28 june , zhongguo qingnian bao )
in law , there are differences between " theoretical circles " and " practical circles . " the former mainly includes " abstract behaviors " such as legal teaching and research , while the latter mostly engage in " concrete actions " such as litigation , legal consultancy , and legal services .
over a long period of time , the law " theoretical circles " and " practical affairs circles " have the phenomenon of " scholars being weaker than civilians . " the " theoretical circle " held that the " practical business circles " lacked necessary legal knowledge and were merely mechanical " legal believers , " while the criticism of the " practical affairs circles " towards the " theoretical circle " pointed out that " theoretical guidance cannot be put into practice . "
as for these differences in the division of labor , the law can be carried out in a neutral manner rather than by giving strong support to either side .
however , the " franchise system " in the " lawyer law " has objectively recognized the " theoretical circle " of the law , which is higher than the " practical business circle " of the law .
as a matter of fact , some experts and scholars engaged in the history of the legal system and the international law of hong kong are purely engaged in the study and teaching of legal theories . their theoretical attainments is totally incompatible with legal practice .
in this way , the " system of licensed lawyers " has undoubtedly created a " bad precedent " for disqualifying the " practical business " of the law .
the superstition of the " theoretical circle " is more than these . for example , the phenomenon of frequently influencing the opinions of experts and the panel discussions of experts will affect or even rejecting court judgments is a direct manifestation of such superstition .
