traffic safety movie enters community construction site in shandong 's jiaozhou city
people 's network qingdao , july 26 th , by reporter xuechun song and correspondent zhongliang fan
from 20 july to 10 august ( monday , 3 , and 5 august ) , the police corps of shandong 's jiaozhou city carried out activities in the city people 's square , the jijia square , the sanhe square , the city 's south district , the lichzhuang square , jiaobei town , jibei town , the dongxian town , the dongxian city industrial district , and the fu'an community .
in the run - up to the film , the traffic police group published a " letter to keep away from traffic accidents and protect life - - a letter to the general public " and some publicity materials . the film also broadcast the " traffic warning on life in traffic accidents " and " on the road to school " special films .
all the tragedies in the show shocked the public and served as a great warning .
in particular , through the cartoon form , primary school students can understand and love the education and receive profound education .
the film attracted more than 3,000 people around the square . in particular , young workers and migrant workers were all sitting in the center of the venue .
as a result of sending safe transportation films to communities ( villages ) and construction sites , the general public also enjoyed movies and received profound education on road safety . the film was warmly welcomed by the residents , especially the new citizens .
health ministry : nationwide health supervision system to be gradually implemented
in order to better implement the " food hygiene law " and the " decision on further strengthening food safety " made by the state council , the ministry of public health has carried out pilot tests on the system of making the food and beverage units public health supervision in 10 regions , including haidian district in beijing , taizhou city in jiangsu , jiang yan city in zhejiang province , luyang city in henan province , wuhan city in hubei province , haikou city in hainan province , sanya city in hainan province , and chengdu in sichuan .
this system will also be gradually implemented throughout the country .
on the basis of routine health supervision , the system of making public health supervision of the catering industry provides on - the - spot supervision and inspection of nine major sanitation issues , including the health permit , health management system , health management personnel , employees ' health certification , food quality and labels , health protection of the food processing process , cleansing and disinfection of the premises , and the procurement of main raw materials .
it is said that the public bulletin will adopt the uniform colours and forms stipulated by the ministry of health , including the results of on - the - spot inspection of nine hygiene conditions , the conclusion of the comprehensive assessment , the views of site hygiene supervisors and the names of the organizations responsible for supervising and supervising on - site hygiene , and the names of the complaint - reporting telephone numbers of customers . it will also be posted at the entrance of the food and beverage units or the customer 's entrance to understand the hygiene conditions of the restaurant .
( by reporter hu qifeng )
un extends mandate of peace - keeping force in ethiopia
the united nations security council today agreed to extend the mandate of the united nations peacekeeping troops in ethiopia and eritrea until january 31 next year .
the resolution called on all parties concerned to honor their commitments , maintain restraint , ease tension , avoid provocative military activities , immediately withdraw their troops and heavy military equipment from the temporary security zone , and urge ethiopia to reduce the number of additional troops recently deployed in the region near the temporary security zone .
the resolution called on ethiopia to take immediate concrete steps to enable the eritrea border committee to rapidly set a border without preconditions , and to request eritrea not to delay the task force 's operations or lift all restrictions imposed on its operations without preconditions .
the resolution reaffirmed full support for the work of the eritrea border committee and welcomed its decision to hold a meeting between the two sides in new york on september 6 .
in 1998 , border conflicts broke out in eritrea and ethiopia , leaving more than 70,000 people dead .
in june 2000 , ethiopia and eritrea signed a cease - fire agreement in algiers , capital of algeria .
in july 2001 , the united nations began to deploy peacekeeping forces in ethiopia and eritrea to monitor the implementation of the cease - fire agreement between the two countries .
( by reporter wu zhiqiang and wang xiang )
county level basketball tournament opens
chengdu , june 30 , 2005
xing coral and reporter tian yuan reported : in order to implement the spirit of the cpc central committee 's instructions on building a harmonious socialist society , in coordination with the building of a socialist new rural area , we publicized the theme of " fitness for all the people and joining the olympic games " to enrich the cultural and sports life of the masses and " welcome the national basketball invitation tournament " in shuangliu county , chengdu city , on 30 august .
the six - day tournament attracted 10 county - level men 's basketball teams from all over the country .
according to the regulations , athletes taking part in the competitions must be amateur athletes aged 18 or above .
professional and professional athletes registered with the state sports general administration 's basketball athletes management center from 2006 to 2007 are not allowed to participate in the competition .
in this competition , the chinese basketball association has adopted the latest set of basketball rules . the competition is divided into two stages , the preliminary and the final stages .
the competition was held by the basketball administration center of the state sports general bureau , the china basketball association , and the china international sports tourism company .
in recent years , the cultural and sports undertakings in shuangliu county , which have a history of over 2,000 years , have developed rapidly . shuangliu county has won a series of honors , such as " an advanced county in national sports " and " an advanced unit in national sports for the masses " .
in particular , in the construction of new villages , shuangliu county has vigorously carried out the peasants ' sports and fitness projects , integrated the construction of sports facilities with rural " beautification , greening , and lighting , " built stadiums in the rural areas , extended the scope of sports services to the rural areas , actively popularized and developed sports and sports competitions with local characteristics , loved and easily participated in by the peasants , and improved the physical quality of the peasants .
modern uniform three major functions
the first is the function of identification .
important signs will be distinguished from the armed forces of different countries , different services and arms , and the armed forces and the general public .
although the use of military uniforms is basically the same among the armies of more than 100 countries in the world , there is no military uniforms of any two countries .
second is symbolic functions .
to a certain extent , military uniforms are a reflection of the spiritual outlook of a country and its national characteristics and also a concentrated embodiment of the combat capability and military qualities of a country 's military .
among the three categories of uniforms , uniforms , and training uniforms , the one that can most fully demonstrate the national and military prestige is quite beautiful .
third is protection functions .
along with the rapid development of new and high - tech weaponry , it has raised the comprehensive defensive functions of the new type of equipment for training . it has enabled its uniform to have various functions , such as defending against bombs , defending against reconnaissance and reconnaissance , chemical , bacterial , and radiation , and its functions of adjusting its temperature , wet , and heat .
