office of the party committee of a certain general unit dares to be more realistic in handling tough issues
chengdu , july 3
qu mao and yang ruyu reported : " we can live in an apartment , thanks to the determination and courage of the party committee office of the group . "
today , more than 10 cadres of a communication training group of the chengdu military region who moved into an apartment building were all elated . they expressed their respect and gratitude for the work style of the " leading members " of the group 's party committee in daring to deal with tough problems in real terms .
a few years ago , with the replacement of personnel , some housing units in the residential buildings of this general unit were occupied in violation of regulations , which made it difficult for cadres on active duty to live in houses . officers and men have a great deal of opinions on this issue .
the group had also cleared their houses several times , but they all failed to settle the problems due to various resistance , thus making this issue an old and difficult one .
" so long as we dare to be more sincere and reasonable , we will not be able to solve any difficult problems . "
after a consensus was reached among the leading members of the new party committee , the principal leaders personally started to thoroughly sort out all the problems of occupying the premises in violation of regulations .
while convincing people with feelings , they hoped that relevant personnel would take the overall situation into consideration and , on the one hand , would explain the relevant policies and regulations concerning military dormitory , fund - raising house , and economical and practical housing , to show the party committee 's firm resolve and principled stand .
with regard to personnel who have housing elsewhere and are unwilling to withdraw from their houses , party committee organs have promptly contacted their units , and have taken corresponding measures to urge them to take the initiative in cooperating with the work of the troops .
after two months of meticulous work , all households in the barracks that violated regulations and occupied houses were moved out of the barracks on schedule , and cadres at the brigade level were given housing according to regulations .
the work style of the party committee of this unit in daring to deal with tough problems has also produced a chain effect . as a result , several cadres who originally were unwilling to actively coordinate with the organization in their assignment have now expressed their willingness to submit themselves to the organizational decision .
