both countries trust each other , support each other , help each other , and closely coordinate with each other in international affairs and in their respective national construction .
china appreciates and thanks bangladesh for its support on the issues of taiwan , human rights , and tibet .
qiao qingchen said that the chinese armed forces treasure the development of friendly relations with the bangladesh armed forces , and expressed the hope that with the joint efforts of both sides , the friendly cooperation between the armed forces of the two countries will be further expanded , and the friendly exchanges and cooperation between the air forces of the two countries will be strengthened to a new level .
bangladesh will make positive efforts to further promote friendly exchanges and cooperation between the two armed forces , especially between the two air forces , he said .
he reiterated that the bangladesh government will , as always , adhere to the one - china policy .
prior to the meeting , qiao qingchen held a ceremony to welcome qi ao 's visit .
qi arrived in beijing on 8 july for an official goodwill visit to china at the invitation of qiao qingchen .
