on june 18 , the guidance course on " psychological warfare under the condition of winning the information warfare " given by lu yuqing , minister of the armed forces of the west town of jingjiang in jiangsu province , was unanimously praised by the participants .
this is a new change made by the city 's people 's armed forces department in light of its actual situation in assigning pressure to specialized military cadres and in focusing on improving the overall quality of military cadres .
at the beginning of this year , the party committee of the people 's armed forces department discovered in its investigation and study of the grass - roots units that some military cadres had too long a term of service and too many positions at the same time had not focused their main efforts on armed work .
for this reason , they have adopted such methods as centralized training , training on behalf of meetings , and relying on the training of local party schools to train specialized military cadres at regular intervals , and have devoted efforts to resolving the problems of narrow knowledge scope and unitary professional quality of specialized arms cadres .
in conjunction with the work of the center , they should be bold in assigning tasks and burdens to cadres specialized in military affairs , and enhance their abilities to work at posts through on - the - job training .
at the same time , they actively coordinated with local organizational departments and jointly formulated a " plan for competitive appointment for specialized arms cadres , " clearly stipulating that armed ministers must be appointed to leading bodies of party committees at the same level and that armed forces ministers must no longer hold other posts concurrently .
we have established a mechanism for the adjustment and exchange of specialized arms cadres , and readjusted and exchanged in good time a number of specialized arms cadres who are aged too old and are not suited to the armed forces work at the grass - roots level , and have promoted and applied them to the comrades with good overall quality and strong work ability .
