public security ministry awarded second - class collective merit to frontier guard hospital of guangdong
xinhua news agency , shenzhen , july 18 ,
li guoliang and huang qi reported : for many years , the hospital of the guangdong frontier guard headquarters has spared no effort in rescuing the people in distress while providing medical services for the troops .
this morning , the ministry of public security held a grand rally in shenzhen to celebrate the second - class collective merit of the guangdong border defense corps hospital and a report meeting on the advanced deeds of supporting the government and cherishing the people .
the hospital of the guangdong frontier guard headquarters has set up three hospitals in phuket , longhua , and baoan , shenzhen specifically targeted at migrant workers . the consultation fee for migrant workers is only 1 yuan . the inspection fee and operation fee are all 20 percent discount .
the hospital has specially provided a " care service vehicle " to help peasant workers receive medical treatment free of charge and introduce a " health service card " for peasant workers . each peasant worker needs only seven yuan per month to receive 12 basic medical check - ups and safeguard .
this measure has benefited more than 12,000 peasant workers .
since 2003 , the hospital has launched a large - scale activity of " lighting up 1,000 lights " for giving medical services to patients . it has organized its eye care personnel to go to such places as tibet , jiangxi , yunnan , and qinghai to " give light and send health " on eight occasions , and has conducted nearly 3,000 cataract operations free of charge , thus bringing the patients back to light .
the armed police forces will change 07 - type costumes from august 1
from august 1 , the armed police force will replace their 07 - type costumes one after another .
today , this reporter saw from the july 7 ceremony for the release of costumes of the armed police force and the demonstration activities that there are 105 varieties in four categories , namely , courtesy , uniform , training uniform , and logo .
the colour of the dress has been adjusted from the existing canary green to the national dress standard .
female officers ' winter uniform will be changed from the closed - eyed hat to the straight - shaped hat , and police officers ' winter uniform will be changed from the closed - collar type to the low - waist type . in spring and autumn uniform will be changed to hunting - type design .
the newly added badges , qualification titles , national defense service regulations , and blue - collar belts , as well as the newly designed cap badge , chest logo , flowers , badges , and armys , have strengthened the function of identifying clothes and enhanced the aesthetic quality .
the armed police 's 07 - type costumes will be changed in three years .
before august 1 , 2007 , the pla will exchange ceremonial uniforms for officers , nonmilitary cadres and national flag guards , military orchestras , and cultural groups , and change spring and autumn uniforms , summer uniforms , and emblems for officers and civilian officers and soldiers stationed in beijing .
in may 2008 , it was a replacement of spring and autumn uniforms , summer uniforms , and logo for other troops and cadets .
in october 2008 , he was given winter uniform and commonly outwear for police officers .
in december 2009 , it replaced winter uniforms for soldiers .
the operation training will be gradually replaced by the usual season starting from 2008 .
the second artillery corps ' base " small , remote , and direct " educational coordination area begins operation
the phenomenon of small , scattered and directly subordinate units being unable to organize education , having limited resources and fighting their own battle will become a history at a base of the second artillery corps .
this reporter recently learned that after six months of experiments , the base issued the " implementation measures for implementing the ' outline of ideological and political education ' " on a trial basis , covering all small , scattered , and directly - administered units on the base and formal operation of certain ideological and political education coordination zones .
in order to promote the effective implementation of the " outline of ideological and political education , " the base at the beginning of the year organized forces to conduct in - depth investigation and study on the current ideological and political education situation in small , scattered and remote units , and sorted out key problems affecting and restricting the time , personnel , and results of education , thus initially forming a new type of educational model for small , scattered , and directly administered units .
the specific method of the joint operation zone is to break the demarcation line of the establishment of a unit , take the lead in assigning a brigade level unit in a relatively concentrated unit in a small , scattered , and directly subordinate unit to a brigade level to conduct unified planning for thematic education , and different units affiliated to the unit either come close to the station to listen to the class or engage in long - distance discussions with the video system .
adopting the method of combining rotation of classes with appointment to posts through competition , unified deployment of educational forces , unified use of educational hardware in each district , sharing and exchanging data and educational experience in each unit , and organizing regular roving reports and sharing of experiences among officers and men of every region .
each co - operation zone has set up full - time educational liaison personnel and part - time educational information collection personnel .
on this basis , the various coordination districts have also established a system for seeking help for difficult problems , jointly discussing major educational topics , reporting on urgent ideological situations , and assessing and appraising problems .
zhang shengmin , director of the political department of the base , told this reporter that the establishment of a political education coordination zone has not only reduced the waste of educational resources but also deepened the results of education .
some political teachers fear that they will lose points in front of the officers and men of other units , take the initiative to study new knowledge , and explore new methods for education .
officers and men who have been educated should also actively absorb the contents of the education , and should not speak out in front of the officers and men of neighboring units when discussing and analyzing the education .
as a result , the enthusiasm of educators and recipients of education has been effectively stimulated .
