( international ) spanish : masked wife arrested
xinhua news agency report of july 7 th from madrid - a spanish woman was attacked by masked bandits . in the struggle , she pulled out the face of the culprits and discovered surprised that the victim was her husband . the police have arrested him .
the woman was working at a noodle shop in the city of valencia , local media reported today .
on one day , a masked man intruded into the shop and , thinking she was a thief , told him to leave a drawer to take money .
however , the man did not take any money but pinch the woman 's neck and wanted to kill her .
she wanted to evade the fate by loading her neck , but the man still did not let her off , or kicked her neck .
in the struggle , the woman pulled down the face cover of the scoundrels but surprised to find that person was actually her husband .
the injured person has been arrested .
the victim told the media that she and her husband were in the process of divorce and they had two children .
thirteen pilots resign from air china wuhan company 's counterlawsuit claims exceed 100 million yuan
xinhua news agency , wuhan , july 11 , by wire ( reporter yangyin liu )
thirteen pilots tendered their resignation , and the " dongjia " china eastern airlines wuhan airlines , ltd. submitted a huge compensation bill totaling 105 - million yuan . this was so far the biggest labor dispute resolution lodged by hubei province in terms of compensation .
the hubei provincial labor dispute arbitration committee is currently examining the case .
in may this year , 13 pilots of the eastern airlines wuhan company submitted their resignation one after another , but the company refused to do so .
the pilot then applied for labor arbitration with the hubei provincial labor dispute arbitration committee in early june , asking for a decision to terminate working relationship with the company of dongdu .
upon receiving the notification of response to the lawsuit , the company lodged a lawsuit and demanded that 13 pilots pay respectively more than 6 million yuan to more than 10 million yuan to the losses caused by the suspension of labor contracts in violation of the labor contract agreement , totaling 105 million yuan .
it has been learned that the pilots signed a fixed - term labor contract with the eastern airlines . except for the conditions for suspension or removal as stipulated in the labor contract , the labor contract validity will continue to reach the legal retirement age of the pilots .
the hubei provincial labor dispute arbitration committee will handle the case in both appeals and counterappeals , and is expected to conclude its hearing before 8 august .
( international ) germany urges russia to pass border treaty with russia
xinhua news agency report of july 12th from lagos ( by staff reporter yang dehong ) - german foreign minister gerhard schroeder , who is visiting latvia , appealed on july 12th to russia for an early passage of the latin american border treaty .
the two sides exchanged views on bilateral relations and cooperation between latvia and the european union , as well as the development of the relations between the european union and russia .
at a press conference held after the talks , stevier called on russia to pass the latin american border treaty as soon as possible .
schneier said : the pace of improvement of relations between latvia and the baltic sea countries and russia is relatively slow . the process of signing the border treaty between latvia and russia has witnessed the course of developing relations between latin america and russia . however , the " historical shadow " may also cause relations between latin america and russia to again retrograde . it is hoped that russia will adopt the latin american border treaty as soon as possible to promote the development of bilateral relations .
on march 27 this year , after 10 years of negotiations , latvian prime minister clerides and russian prime minister fradkov signed the border treaty in moscow .
on 17 may , the latin american parliament passed the latin american border treaty .
according to latvian media reports , the russian parliament will vote on the treaty in the near future .
( international ) dprk , rok to hold sixth meeting
xinhua news agency , pyongyang , july 16 , by wire ( reporter haorong xia )
the military representatives of the democratic people 's republic of korea ( dprk ) and the republic of korea ( rok ) held a routine military meeting at panmunjon on 16 august . the two sides agreed to hold the sixth round of talks between the 24 th and 26 th .
according to a report by the korean central news agency , pak lin - soo , a military representative of the dprk and a senior colonel of the dprk people 's army , put forward a proposal of setting up a joint fishing area between yanping island and bailing island in the western part of the dprk , and gave a detailed explanation of the proposal .
he said : to establish a joint fishing zone , we must implement the principle of seeking the greatest common prosperity of the nation and safeguarding peace and stability .
on the issue of sea demarcation , pak lin - soo said : in order to prevent a military conflict between the two sides in the western region , the two sides should abandon their respective maritime boundaries that they have upheld so far , acknowledge and respect each other 's maritime power , and take the relevant agreement between the dprk and the rok , the korean armistice agreement , and the internationally recognized laws as the basis for consultation .
he said that it is the dprk military 's " consistent stand " to promptly formulate military safeguard measures to promote cooperation and exchanges between the dprk and the rok .
he said : at present , the rok side should take military measures to ensure that nongovernmental vessels can directly leave the dprk port for the south and sail freely across the cheju strait .
this is the second routine contact between the dprk and the rok since 10 april .
the fifth meeting between the dprk and the rok was held from 8 to 11 may at the " reunification cabinet " of the dprk side at panmunjon .
