at a meeting on 28 august in beijing to examine projects of selecting , training , and application of new olympic flowers and plants , experts have come to the conclusion that adopting the promotion and cultivation of new technology , different types of flowers and plants during the natural flower period can bloom in the same summer period , and the results of their appreciation in august at the beijing olympics will be the best .
