as a result , many people misunderstand that bananas can suffer from cancer . as a result , the prices of bananas in hainan have fallen dramatically .
the above two reports have both caused a sensation because they directly touched the most sensitive issue in people 's nerve , that is , the issue of food safety .
if the media said that so - and - so food would endanger health , then it would surely spread all the time , and people would generally adopt a more trusting and unbelievable attitude toward the objects involved . as far as a person is concerned , having fewer watermelon and bananas in hainan could not be counted as anything extraordinary , but they would have a great impact on the production and sales of the products .
