nanjing subway drivers urged to undergo psychological adjustment
key word : psychological adjustment
according to a xinhua news agency report , on the evening of 3 july , an explosion occurred at the nanjing subway in which a slew of people died .
according to this reporter 's description , " zhu zhengting , 22 , a young subway driver , encountered a nightmare . when i saw him yesterday , i seemed to have not yet turned his god from fear into a seat , sat straight to the air , and the expression in his eyes looked somewhat in a trance . "
obviously , the spirit of this young driver was greatly affected , and he badly needed to undergo a psychological restructuring , otherwise he would bring harm to his life .
do you still remember that more than 10 years ago , the rescue worker who rescued a girl from an abandoned oil well in durao , the united states finally chose to commit suicide after enduring long - term mental torment .
at that time , although he had a simple psychological adjustment , because people focused more attention on the rescued little girl , he ignored the people who needed more psychological adjustment and finally could not avoid the occurrence of tragedies .
similarly , a few years ago , the british policeman who opened a container in the dover strait was reportedly shocked at the scene .
it was only after more than two months of psychological adjustments by the british side that brought him back to normal .
people will suffer extremely great psychological harm after being stimulated by disasters . at this time , relying on personal strength alone will be very difficult to completely recover and often leave behind psychological wounds .
since it is hard for outsiders to discover this injury and find out that there is no way to do it , many of those involved will suffer all their lives .
however , it is not enough for the people of our country to show concern for psychological wounds . in particular , the families or departments in charge of the matter often think of it after losing the best period . it is already too late at that time .
after the media become diversified , we often hear about some hacker incidents that have harmed many female teenagers , and many young children have seen the cruel harm done to their parents .
after these young people were rescued , very few people heard that they had received psychological treatment , and more often than not , they were relieved by family love and comfort .
although the victims can feel that they are safe , the injury they have suffered has become a wound that can never be cured , and will be awakened at all times and affect the lives of the victims .
it is fortunate that the driver 's leadership immediately persuaded him and relieved him of his mental pressure .
after all , the responsibility for the accident is not with the driver , and the driver has taken measures when he found out the situation . what he should do is not stop the occurrence of the tragedy .
it is believed that even if they were not the drivers concerned , anyone at the scene would be intimidated by the accident .
however , other people have no responsibility to commit suicide , even though they have been intimidated , they will gradually be forgotten as time develops .
the drivers concerned are not so fortunate that they must remember that they will probably remember for a whole life .
if he can extricate himself from this state of mind , even if he can not extricate himself from life , he will often be subjected to such a shock and scare .
modern health concepts are more comprehensive than in the past , and mental health is beginning to attract people 's attention .
it is regrettable that the spiritual state of mankind is very disheartedness . especially in the cities , people 's mental health is extremely poor , and the majority of people have more or less hidden dangers in their minds . however , some people have encountered problems and have failed to pay sufficient attention to them .
just think of the lesson of the " yang lijuan incident " in the previous stage , some irresponsible media regarded a patient being tortured by mental problems as a target of speculation , which had a very bad social impact .
in the future , we should avoid such incidents from happening , otherwise our society will truly become a morbid society .
